lead_paragraph: The martial art of muaythai and cheerleading, with its strong youth appeal, received provisional recognition as Olympic sports by the International Olympic Committee on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Muaythai, Cheerleading Granted Provisional Olympic Status
